        <p>Stefan Bohacek has been working for years to enable almost anyone to create simple, automated bots, offering
          up everything from a constantly-updated view of the weather at the South Pole to one that posts excerpts from
          the City of New York's archives of civic data (here's a map of every Latin cultural organization in the city!)
          to ones that post obscure and delightful images from the collections of museums around the world.</p>
        <cite>
